title: Strictly Come Dancing 2019 contestants: judges send David James packing after dance-off with Mike Bushell
text:
The BBC's ballroom competition, Strictly Come Dancing, is cha-cha-ing through its 17th series, with Tess Daly and Claudia Winkleman back on presenting duties, while Zoe Ball is this year joined by Rylan Clark-Neal to co-present daily sister show It Takes Two.

Judges Bruno Tonioli, Shirley Ballas and Craig Revel-Horwood are joined by a new face on the panel - Motsi Mabuse, sister of pro dancer Oti, who replaces Darcey Bussell.

Professional dancers AJ Pritchard, Katya Jones, Aljaž Skorjanec, Amy Dowden, Anton Du Beke, Janette Manrara, Neil Jones, Oti Mabuse, Kevin Clifton, Karen Clifton, Nadiya Bychkova, Graziano Di Prima, Gorka Marquez, Johannes Radebe, Luba Mushtuk, Giovanni Pernice and Dianne Buswell welcome a new addition too - Nancy Xu, who replaces Pasha Kovalev.
